 <span data-ttu-id="cd3db-275">Другие параметры конфигурации выходных данных, см. в разделе <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SetOutputToAudioStream%2A>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SetOutputToNull%2A>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SetOutputToWaveFile%2A>, и <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SetOutputToWaveStream%2A> методы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cd3db-275">For other output configuration options, see the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SetOutputToAudioStream%2A>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SetOutputToNull%2A>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SetOutputToWaveFile%2A>, and <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SetOutputToWaveStream%2A> methods.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="cd3db-276">В следующем примере синтезатор произнести фразу, чтобы звуковые выходные данные по умолчанию.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cd3db-276">The following example uses the synthesizer to speak a phrase to the default audio output.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System;  
using System.Speech.Synthesis;  
  
namespace SampleSynthesis  
{  
  class Program  
  {  
    static void Main(string[] args)  
    {  
  
